    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Guide Lumm-e in this charming 2D puzzle game. Use your flashlight to grow mushrooms into platforms, lights, and elevators. Solve puzzles to heal the world's disease in a relaxing, game jam-winning adventure. No precision platforming required!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As one of the devs said: <i>&quot;A relaxing post-apocalyptic game!&quot;</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use your flashlight</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mushrooms react to light from your flashlight. This is the key gameplay mechanic of the game! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031050/extras/014b4e20c94fbacabfdc66200b38f919.poster.avif?t=1732533246\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031050/extras/014b4e20c94fbacabfdc66200b38f919.webm?t=1732533246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031050/extras/014b4e20c94fbacabfdc66200b38f919.mp4?t=1732533246\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Create your own platforms</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ride on platforms that grow from mushrooms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031050/extras/92d931fd18c37aab4d499d8c306f5f50.poster.avif?t=1732533246\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031050/extras/92d931fd18c37aab4d499d8c306f5f50.webm?t=1732533246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031050/extras/92d931fd18c37aab4d499d8c306f5f50.mp4?t=1732533246\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Light based puzzles</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Objects in this game interact with light. This makes for refreshing and clever puzzles.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031050/extras/33fba881881b36933e11c9b980d9b4e8.poster.avif?t=1732533246\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031050/extras/33fba881881b36933e11c9b980d9b4e8.webm?t=1732533246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031050/extras/33fba881881b36933e11c9b980d9b4e8.mp4?t=1732533246\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
